封聖wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"兩個都係中共自選自聖  <br />\n咁岩又係2個人  <br />\n教廷對大紅龍鳩軟 <br />\n<br />\n成件事發展睇落真係一樣樣<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係睇下教廷幾時瓦解"},{"pid":"98b6285c21f1538d2c70b1b0d4080181f5c38962","tid":549032,"uid":65023,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"樓主洞察力好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ffd7e42d5b42937cf1b27a6d539712a01062f4","tid":549032,"uid":107874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b6285c21f1538d2c70b1b0d4080181f5c38962","tid":549032,"uid":65023,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"樓主洞察力好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"美極巴 有無網或書介紹下"},{"pid":"3209537730b097165c932db6d564efaf65fd2c62","tid":549032,"uid":90704,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"我都覺得好似<br />\n中共用權力金錢女人去腐化全世界<br />\n不斷試探引誘 根本就是聖經入面既撒旦<br />\n<br />\n但我真係唔認同你對馬克思既評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029a948a0baa0e795dab9db2ce919e5b9eef03d7","tid":549032,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6f009699ab151cdc73a8f8210b797197970b38","tid":549032,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"啟示錄12:3 天上又現出異象來．有一條大紅龍、七頭十角、七頭上戴著七個冠冕。<br />\n大紅龍 = 中共<br />\n七頭 = 柒頭<br />\n十角 = ??<br />\n七個冠冕 = 軍政大權集於一身"},{"pid":"ea532abab02c4c9115691327e82a7709f8e513da","tid":549032,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/195843_a54afa3700d87eee8373c9c34bd1921d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservic